#: ../../faq.rst:12 370a7124b7354355a7ee5c491ecacc6b
msgid "Triton errors on Windows"
msgstr "Windows 上的 Triton 错误"

#: ../../faq.rst:14 8cec725dd9364945a24c451aec2b4fdb
msgid ""
"**Symptom:** ``Python int too large to convert to C long`` or Triton-"
"related import failures when loading the model on Windows."
msgstr "**现象：** 在 Windows 上加载模型时出现 ``Python int too large to convert to C long``，或与 Triton 相关的导入失败。"

#: ../../faq.rst:16 99868fb6868f461a90a4aa6524900d5d
msgid ""
"**Cause:** Triton has limited Windows support, and certain PyTorch + "
"Triton version combinations trigger known bugs."
msgstr "**原因：** Triton 对 Windows 的支持较有限，某些 PyTorch 与 Triton 的版本组合会触发已知问题。"

#: ../../faq.rst:18 ../../faq.rst:55 ../../faq.rst:86 ../../faq.rst:185
