#: ../../faq.rst:43 ff6ecaddd71944939a75e54409c4ec87
msgid ""
"This disables ``torch.compile`` acceleration. Inference will be slower "
"but functionally correct."
msgstr "这会禁用 ``torch.compile`` 加速。推理速度会变慢，但功能上是正确可用的。"

