#: ../../faq.rst:115 4417faf5129b428a84d35b82c04a0db0
msgid "Mac / MPS support"
msgstr "Mac / MPS 支持"

#: ../../faq.rst:117 203c52fc38f84be6b63624bc321b1f7c
msgid "**Q: Can VoxCPM run on Mac (Apple Silicon)?**"
msgstr "**问：VoxCPM 可以在 Mac（Apple Silicon）上运行吗？**"

#: ../../faq.rst:119 7edb065dc9394b2681fbc4a701680413
msgid ""
"Yes. VoxCPM supports CPU and MPS (Metal Performance Shaders) on Apple "
"Silicon Macs (`#14 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/14>`_, `#20 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/20>`_, `#41 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/41>`_)."
msgstr "可以。VoxCPM 支持在 Apple Silicon Mac 上使用 CPU 和 MPS（Metal Performance Shaders）（参见 `#14 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/14>`_、`#20 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/20>`_、`#41 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/41>`_）。"

#: ../../faq.rst:121 0624e172f1854f86aa4719c1f04c37be
msgid ""
"**CPU:** Works out of the box, but inference is slow (`#67 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/67>`_)."
msgstr "**CPU：** 开箱即用，但推理速度较慢（参见 `#67 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/67>`_）。"

#: ../../faq.rst:122 fee4d61d814f436e9848aff9d3af1801
msgid ""
"**MPS:** Supported for accelerated inference. Load the model normally and"
" it will automatically detect MPS if available."
msgstr "**MPS：** 支持加速推理。正常加载模型即可，若系统可用，它会自动检测并使用 MPS。"

#: ../../faq.rst:126 03fbc5a4ee5c4b0fa3f650878dc52a4c
msgid ""
"The denoiser (ZipEnhancer) runs on CPU even when MPS is active. If you "
"don't need prompt speech enhancement, set ``load_denoiser=False`` to save"
" memory."
msgstr "即使启用了 MPS，降噪器（ZipEnhancer）仍然运行在 CPU 上。如果你不需要增强 prompt 语音，可设置 ``load_denoiser=False`` 以节省内存。"

