"VoxCPM is most tested on **Python 3.10–3.11**. For current releases, "
"**Python 3.10–3.12** is the recommended runtime range. Known issues:"
msgstr "VoxCPM 在 **Python 3.10–3.11** 上测试最充分。对于当前版本，推荐的运行范围是 **Python 3.10–3.12**。已知问题如下："

#: ../../faq.rst:134 3fb0603b838146a78675f479ca3fe0da
msgid ""
"**Python 3.14+:** Installation may fail due to dependency "
"incompatibilities (`#176 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/176>`_). Use Python 3.10–3.12 "
"instead."
msgstr "**Python 3.14+：** 由于依赖不兼容，安装可能失败（参见 `#176 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/176>`_）。请改用 Python 3.10–3.12。"

